g.text: Perennial Task - A simple command-line task manager.
create Interactively or non-interactively create a new task.
edit [task_file] Edit a task. Select from a list or specify a file.
complete [task_file] Mark a task as complete.
describe [task_file] Show a detailed description of a task.
history [task_file] Show the full completion history of a single task.
report [date] Show a report of all due and upcoming tasks.
help [command] Show this help message, or help for a specific command.
